<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244147>
    dc:description "FIGURES 49A–I. Hexapopha gunma sp. nov., male, SEM images (MPEG 37861; PBI_OON 45704). A–B carapace. A lateral view. B ventral view. C–D mouthparts. C lateral view. D lateral view. E left endite, detail of projections. F abdomen, ventral view. G–I embolus. G prolateral view. H retrolateral view. I ventral view. Abbreviations: mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244147/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244155>
    dc:description "FIGURES 52A–L. Hexapopha corniculata sp. nov., SEM images. A–H male (MPEG 19425; PBI_OON 43846). I–L female (MPEG 10823; PBI_OON 45133). A habitus, lateral view. B carapace, ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D–E left palp. D prolateral view. E retrolateral view. F sperm pore, ventral view. G–H embolus. G prolateral view. H retrolateral view. I carapace, anterior view. J mouthparts, ventral view. K epigastric region, ventral view. L internal genitalia, dorsal view. Abbreviations: as, anterior sclerite; mp, median projection; P, projection; vs, ventral surface of distal hook of posterior sclerite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244155/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244159>
    dc:description "FIGURES 53A–I. Hexapopha egua sp. nov., male (MPEG 10863; PBI_OON 45817). A–B habitus. A dorsal view. B lateral view. C–E carapace. C dorsal view. D ventral view. E anterior view. F mouthparts, ventral view. G abdomen, ventral view. H–I left palp. H prolateral view. I retrolateral view. Scale bars: 0.1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244161>
    dc:description "FIGURES 54A–L. Hexapopha egua sp. nov., male, SEM images (MPEG 10856; PBI_OON 45350). A–B carapace. A lateral view. B ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D–E endites. D ventral view. E lateral view. F abdomen, ventral view. G sperm pore, ventral view. H–I left palp. H prolateral view. I retrolateral view. J–L embolus. J prolateral view. K retrolateral view. L ventral view. Abbreviations: mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244161/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8244171>
    dc:description "FIGURES 57A–L. Hexapopha izquierdoi sp. nov., SEM images. A–H male (MPEG 37810; PBI_OON 45602). I–L female (MPEG 37834; PBI_OON 45776). A–B carapace. A lateral view. B ventral view. C mouthparts, ventral view. D–E endites. D ventral view.E lateral view.F left palp, retrolateral view. G–H embolus. G prolateral view.H retrolateral view.I carapace, ventral view. J epigastric region, ventral view. K internal genitalia, dorsal view. L right endite, detail of serrula (arrow). Abbreviations: mp, median projection; P, projection." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8244171/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

